From: Li Jun <jun.li@freescale.com>
Date: Tue, 27 Jan 2015 17:26:48 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1451/1543] MLK-10101-5 usb: chipidea: otg: init otg_fsm of
 usb_bus while start host

commit 23a6878bbc8cc9be88dd0dd26792bf199bf5f93c from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git

Set otg_fsm of usb_bus to be ci->fsm while start host.

Signed-off-by: Li Jun <jun.li@freescale.com>
---
 drivers/usb/chipidea/host.c |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/usb/chipidea/host.c b/drivers/usb/chipidea/host.c
index 40131e4..85febf7 100644
--- a/drivers/usb/chipidea/host.c
+++ b/drivers/usb/chipidea/host.c
@@ -264,6 +264,7 @@ static int host_start(struct ci_hdrc *ci)
 		ci->hcd = hcd;
 
 		if (ci_otg_is_fsm_mode(ci)) {
+			hcd->self.otg_fsm = &ci->fsm;
 			otg->host = &hcd->self;
 			hcd->self.otg_port = 1;
 		}
